text: Pyhäjärvi is a town in Northern Ostrobothnia, Finland. As of 28 February 2023, 4,813 people lived there. Neighbouring municipalities are Haapajärvi, Kiuruvesi, Kärsämäki, Pielavesi, Pihtipudas and Pyhäntä. == Other websites == * Town of Pyhäjärvi – Official website Category:Municipalities of North Ostrobothnia
title: Pyhäjärvi
